Package: framerd
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Scalable knowledge base development and application platform
 FramerD provides a robust and scalable object database especially
 designed and optimized for pointer-intensive semi-structured data with
 complex or evolving data models.  FramerD includes full support for
 Unicode in both data and programs together with powerful tools for
 text processing and linguistic analysis.
 FramerD natively supports reading and and generation of XML, HTML, and
 MIME data.  Web services support has long included built-in support
 for processing CGI requests both directly and with fastcgi.  With
 version 2.4, FramerD comes with mod_fdserv, a lightweight extension to
 the Apache webserver for transparently managing persistent
 multi-threaded servlets responding to CGI requests.

Package: framerd-bin
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Binaries for FramerD release

Package: framerd-modules
Architecture: any
Depends: framerd-bin (> ${binary:Version})

Package: framerd-apache
Architecture: any
Depends: framerd-bin (= ${binary:Version})
Description: The mod_fdserv module for FramerD servlets under Apache

Package: framerd-mysql
Architecture: any
Depends: framerd-bin (= ${binary:Version})
Description: MYSQL bindings for FramerD

Package: framerd-sqlite
Architecture: any
Depends: framerd-bin (= ${binary:Version})
Description: SQLite bindings for FramerD

Package: framerd-imagetools
Architecture: any
Depends: framerd-bin (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Image tools for FramerD
  Bindings to various image libraries modules for FramerD,
  including ImageMagick, QRCode generation, and EXIF extraction.

Package: framerd-markdown
Architecture: any
Depends: framerd-bin (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Markdown conversion (bindings) for FramerD

Package: framerd-tidy
Architecture: any
Depends: framerd-bin (= ${binary:Version})
Description: HTML Tidy (bindings) for FramerD

Package: framerd-doc
Architecture: all
Description: documentation for framerd

